---
description: No hardcoded UI strings; lang files and meta for JS
alwaysApply: true
---

# TRANSLATIONS

✔
```php
__('messages.success')
```

✔ (Blade)
```blade
@lang('messages.success')
```

✖
```php
echo "Success";
```

- NO hardcoded text
- ALWAYS use lang files
- PHP/Blade: use `@lang()`
- JavaScript: use meta tags  
  ```html
  <meta name="trans-key" content="{{ @lang('messages.success') }}">
  ```
  ```js
  $('meta[name="trans-key"]').attr('content')
  ```
